			</div>
		</div>
	</div>

	<div class="contact-container">
		<div class="contact-header fade-in">
			<div class="section-badge">
				<span>
					<svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" style="margin-right: 6px; vertical-align: middle;">
						<path d="M22 16.92V20C22 20.5304 21.7893 21.0391 21.4142 21.4142C21.0391 21.7893 20.5304 22 20 22H4C3.46957 22 2.96086 21.7893 2.58579 21.4142C2.21071 21.0391 2 20.5304 2 20V16.92C3.65 15.64 5.58 14.69 7.62 14.18C9.66 13.67 11.81 13.41 14 13.41C16.19 13.41 18.34 13.67 20.38 14.18C22.42 14.69 24.35 15.64 26 16.92" stroke="#25c1ce" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
						<path d="M6 8C7.10457 8 8 7.10457 8 6C8 4.89543 7.10457 4 6 4C4.89543 4 4 4.89543 4 6C4 7.10457 4.89543 8 6 8Z" stroke="#25c1ce" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
						<path d="M18 8C19.1046 8 20 7.10457 20 6C20 4.89543 19.1046 4 18 4C16.8954 4 16 4.89543 16 6C16 7.10457 16.8954 8 18 8Z" stroke="#25c1ce" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
					</svg>
					CONTACT ONS
				</span>
			</div>
			<h2 class="section-title">
				Neem <span class="highlight">Contact</span> Op
			</h2>
			<p class="section-description">
				Heeft u vragen over beveiliging? Wij helpen u graag met persoonlijk advies
			</p>
		</div>

		<div class="contact-content">
			<div class="contact-info fade-in">
				<div class="info-card">
					<div class="info-icon">
						<svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
							<path d="M21 10C21 17 18 20 12 20C11.27 20 10.53 19.82 9.75 19.5L6 22V18.5C4.55 17.71 3.5 16.08 3.5 14C3.5 9 6.5 5 12 5C17.5 5 21 9 21 10Z" stroke="#25c1ce" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
							<circle cx="12" cy="12" r="1" fill="#25c1ce"/>
						</svg>
					</div>
					<div class="info-content">
						<h4>Bezoekadres</h4>
						<p>
							Zuidelijke Dwarsweg 110<br/>
							8111 AD HEERENVEEN<br/>
							Nederland
						</p>
					</div>
				</div>

				<div class="info-card">
					<div class="info-icon">
						<svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
							<path d="M22 16.92V20C22 20.5304 21.7893 21.0391 21.4142 21.4142C21.0391 21.7893 20.5304 22 20 22H4C3.46957 22 2.96086 21.7893 2.58579 21.4142C2.21071 21.0391 2 20.5304 2 20V16.92C3.65 15.64 5.58 14.69 7.62 14.18C9.66 13.67 11.81 13.41 14 13.41C16.19 13.41 18.34 13.67 20.38 14.18C22.42 14.69 24.35 15.64 26 16.92" stroke="#25c1ce" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
							<path d="M6 8C7.10457 8 8 7.10457 8 6C8 4.89543 7.10457 4 6 4C4.89543 4 4 4.89543 4 6C4 7.10457 4.89543 8 6 8Z" stroke="#25c1ce" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
